data.description: Beautiful single-story home like new with a smart layout. 3 Bedrooms located in the front and the 4th primary bedroom separate to the back of the home with large walk-in closet. Open floor plan with granite counter tops, Great home for entertaining. Located 10 minutes from downtown and 5 minutes from Brooks City Base shopping and dining. Seller will help with some closing costs.
